E-Commerce Platform — Structured Project Plan
Last updated: June 2026
Branch: shopping-module

Companion doc: FEATURE_ROADMAP.md (detailed APIs, DDL, file checklists, business rules)

API style (current):  Legacy verb-in-path + header-based IDs (user_id, product_id)
API style (target):   RESTful paths with path variables
Auth (target):        JWT + Spring Security before production orders

