PHASE 0: PREREQUISITES (1–2 Weeks)
================================================================================
Status: ✅ COMPLETE

Comfortable with:
- Java 21, OOP, Collections, Streams, Exception Handling
- JDBC, SQL, CRUD APIs, Validation API

================================================================================
PHASE 1: SETUP THE FOUNDATION
================================================================================
Status: ✅ COMPLETE

Tech stack in use:
- Java 21, Spring Boot 3.x, Maven
- Spring Data JPA, PostgreSQL, Lombok, Validation API
- IntelliJ, Postman, Git, GitHub

Project structure (actual):
  ecommerce/
   ├── controller/     User, Address, Category, Product, Cart, Health
   ├── service/        User, Address, Category, Product, Cart
   ├── repository/     IUser, IAddress, ICategory, IProduct, ICart, ICartItem
   ├── entity/         User, Address, Category, Product, Cart, CartItem
   ├── dto/            user, address, category, product, cart, common
   ├── exception/      GlobalExceptionHandler + domain exceptions
   ├── configs/        EndpointPrinter, StartupSummaryPrinter
   └── enums/          AddressType

Branches merged into shopping-module:
- Setup-the-Foundation  → users, base project
- address-module        → addresses
- product-module        → categories + products
- shopping-module       → cart schema + cart Java

Base URL: /ecommerce/v1

Patterns in use:
- Lombok entities and DTOs
- @Service + @RequiredArgsConstructor injection
- JpaRepository with derived query methods
- Inline toResponseDto() mapping in services
- GlobalExceptionHandler for domain exceptions

Learn (completed):
- Spring Boot Basics, Dependency Injection, Bean Lifecycle
- REST APIs, JPA & Hibernate, DTO Pattern

================================================================================
PHASE 2: DATABASE DESIGN
================================================================================
Status: ✅ COMPLETE (schema.sql)

Tables — DDL + seed data:
  users           ✅  → UserEntity
  addresses       ✅  → AddressEntity       (FK → users)
  categories      ✅  → CategoryEntity
  products        ✅  → ProductEntity      (FK → categories)
  cart            ✅  → CartEntity         (UNIQUE user_id, FK → users)
  cart_items      ✅  → CartItemEntity     (FK → cart, products)
  orders          ✅  DDL only              (order_number, payment_status, address FKs)
  order_items     ✅  DDL only              (price snapshot at checkout)

JPA entities missing: OrderEntity, OrderItemEntity
Relationships: Long FK columns (not @ManyToOne mappings yet)

Learn (completed):
- OneToMany, ManyToOne via FK design, constraints, indexes

================================================================================
MODULE-BY-MODULE — IMPLEMENTED APIs (actual paths)
================================================================================

USERS  ✅  /ecommerce/v1/users
  POST   /createUser
  GET    /all, /user              (header: user_id)
  PATCH  /updateUser, /isActive
  DELETE /deleteUser              (header: user_id)
  Exceptions: UserNotFoundException, UserAlreadyExistsException

ADDRESSES  ✅  /ecommerce/v1/addresses
  POST   /createAddress
  GET    /all, /addressId, /userAddress
  PATCH  /updateAddress
  DELETE /deleteAddress
  Enum: AddressType (SHIPPING, BILLING, OFFICE, HOME, OTHER)

CATEGORIES  ✅  /ecommerce/v1/categories
  POST   /createCategory
  GET    /all, /categoryId, /getCategory
  PATCH  /updateCategory
  DELETE /deleteCategoryById, /deleteCategoryByName

PRODUCTS  ✅  /ecommerce/v1/products
  POST   /addProduct
  GET    /all, /productId, /productByName, /productsByCategoryId
  PATCH  /updateProduct
  DELETE /productId                (header: product_id)
  Category validation on add / update / list-by-category
  Exceptions: ProductNotFoundException, CategoryNotFoundException

CART  ✅  /ecommerce/v1/cart
  POST   /createCart, /addItem
  GET    /getCart                  (header: user_id)
  PATCH  /updateQuantity
  DELETE /removeItem
  Rules: one cart per user, stock checks, merge duplicates, computed totals
  Exceptions: CartNotFoundException, CartItemNotFoundException, OutOfStockException

HEALTH  ✅
  GET    /                         → welcome message

