  [x] ProductNotFoundException, CategoryNotFoundException with messages
  [x] UserNotFoundException, UserAlreadyExistsException
  [x] CartNotFoundException, CartItemNotFoundException, OutOfStockException
  [x] UserService.getUserById returns DTO; email update bug fixed
  [x] AddressController.getAddressesByUserId calls addressService
  [x] Product module returns DTOs; category validation on add/update
