High priority (remaining):
  [ ] UserController.updateUser — DTO + @Valid (not raw Map)
  [ ] UserRequestDto — @NotNull on required create fields
  [ ] AddressRequestDto — align NOT NULL with DB (city, state, pinCode, country)
  [ ] AddressService.createAddress — validate user exists
  [ ] AddressService.getAddressesByUserId — return [] when empty
  [ ] ProductService.addProduct — default stockQuantity to 0 if null
  [ ] deleteUser / deleteProduct / deleteCategory — FK-safe or 409 errors

Medium priority (remaining):
  [ ] Return DTOs from Category/Address GET /all (still return entities)
  [ ] ProductRequestDto.productId @NotNull for update
  [ ] Remove duplicate dto/cartItem/ package
  [ ] AddressNotFoundException + handler
  [ ] Replace RuntimeException in CategoryService, AddressService
  [ ] Handler for DataIntegrityViolationException (FK failures → 409)

